quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  29,1,"Alif. Lam. Mim."
  29,2,"Do people think that they will be let go merely by saying: “We believe,” and that they will not be tested,",footnotes:180061:1
  29,3,"for We indeed tested those who went before them? Allah will most certainly ascertain those who spoke the truth and those who lied.",footnotes:180062:1,footnotes:180063:2
  29,4,"Do the evil-doers suppose that they will get the better of Us? How evil is their judgement!",footnotes:180064:1,footnotes:180065:2
  29,5,"Let him who looks forward to meeting Allah know that Allah's appointed term will surely come to pass. He is All-Hearing, All-Knowing.",footnotes:180066:1,footnotes:180067:2
  29,6,"Whosoever strives(in the cause of Allah) does so to his own good. Surely Allah stands in no need of anyone in the whole Universe.",footnotes:180068:1,footnotes:180069:2